this is my code to apply dark theme, it doesn't always work nice:
```
// ==UserScript==
// @name         dark
// @namespace    http://tampermonkey.net/
// @version      0.1
// @description  apply dark theme to any site
// @author       beenotung
// @match        https://*
// @grant        none
// ==/UserScript==

(function () {
'use strict';
  var bg='black';
  var color='lightgreen';
  var e=document.createElement('style');
  e.innerHTML="*{\
    background: black !important;\
    color: lightgreen !important;\
  }";
  document.head.append(e);
})();
```
In the "User includes" session, add "http://*" and "https://*"

